    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "attacking a knocked down opponent (in a fighting game)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "格闘ゲームで、倒れた相手に追撃する「死体蹴り」は卑怯だと批判されることもある。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼は、相手がダウンした隙をついて、効果的な「死体蹴り」を決めた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「そんな戦法、死体蹴りじゃないか！」と、敗者は不満を漏らした。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "kicking someone when they are down",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "一度失敗した人をさらに貶めるのは、まるで「死体蹴り」だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "彼の批判は、すでに落ち込んでいる相手への「死体蹴り」のように聞こえた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「弱っている者に追い打ちをかけるのは、死体蹴りと同じだ」と恩師は語った。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
